{"tid":1489145,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Facebook與Twitter 均發現存在來自受中國政府操控的、具有協調性、非真實性的互聯網資訊傳播","createTime":"2019-08-19T20:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T11:01:09.000Z","uid":50294,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"81ea78e21a83a578892e3051b83c24606cdea79e","tid":1489145,"uid":50294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T20:47:36.000Z","msg":"Facebook與Twitter今天分別發聲明，指兩家社交媒體平台均發現存在來自受中國政府操控的、具有協調性、非真實性的互聯網資訊傳播，其目的在於針對近期香港的示威遊行活動。參與這些社交媒體行動的有關帳戶涉及許多造假行為，包括以虛假帳戶管理所謂的新聞媒體專頁。有關行動經常通過不同方式發布與香港政治與近期遊行活動相關的虛假資訊。Facebook和Twitter的調查結果顯示這些行動與中國政府有關，Twitter認為是這些行動受到中國政府協調與支持，從兩家平台揭露的一些案例可以看出，有關行動明顯旨在詆毀香港示威者和行動目的，更將示威者形容為恐怖份子，顛倒黑白。<br />\n <br />\n<strong>Facebook聲明：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://newsroom.fb.com/news/2019/08/removing-cib-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2F08%2Fremoving-cib-china%2F&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex1mNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=8189be1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://newsroom.fb.com/news/2019/08/removing-cib-china/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Twitter聲明：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.twitter.com/en_us/topics/company/2019/information_operations_directed_at_Hong_Kong.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.twitter.com%2Fen_us%2Ftopics%2Fcompany%2F2019%2Finformation_operations_directed_at_Hong_Kong.html&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex1mNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=ebab3376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.twitter.com/en_us/topics/company/2019/information_operations_directed_at_Hong_Kong.html</a>"},{"pid":"c7fc63541abb0013b9ea3f677eaaa5050fe2b786","tid":1489145,"uid":187972,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T20:52:24.000Z","msg":"FB都Ban咗唔少我地呢邊嘅AC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061a1052d4b141cca33f3aa7bc63e95f23a60401","tid":1489145,"uid":51938,"like